{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shotgun Farmers</strong> is the online multiplayer shooter where missed shots grow guns. Fire your bullets into the ground to plant your ammo. Reloading isn\u2019t an option, so grab one of the deadly crops planted by the bullets of you and your enemies. Shot at by a sniper? Well they just planted you your very own sniper gun to fire back with!  Harvest weapon plants quickly for more ammo or let them grow for a larger clip.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/604240/extras/key_shot_OP.gif?t=1732218882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle enemy farmers in different game modes that change the way you play. Chase a chicken around the map in Chicken Run, steal the enemy\u2019s prized pig in Capture The Pig, defend the scarecrow in King of the Crow, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/604240/extras/chicken_pig_wide.gif?t=1732218882\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR FARMER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up your farmer and complete challenges to unlock hats, shovel skins, costumes, and emotes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/604240/extras/cosmetics_wide.gif?t=1732218882\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE THE HORDE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle zombies in Horde Mode where you take on waves of infected farmers and animals. Can you survive to the end and take on the final boss? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAY ONLINE OR OFFLINE </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play online with up to 10 players per match, in public lobbies and private rooms. Take on AI bots in Practice Mode to sharpen your farming skills offline or squad up with your friends and take on other players online. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FREQUENT UPDATES </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shotgun Farmers is updated regularly with free updates that bring new weapons, new cosmetics, limited time game modes, and more new maps to come!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Seeds of War","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/95d3b33ab1218481571fe3aad485afe0bb48fd32.jpg"},{"name":"Carrocketeer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/2675efd9678bb9e88c495c1c9dd279fbf15b6b17.jpg"},{"name":"No Diggity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/4000b382f76c73fcf3dde8eca12a34e2ae3ba5d7.jpg"},{"name":"Easy Peasy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/00c507db2790fc4c042da74f7154d4467ad464b5.jpg"},{"name":"Cornivore","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/52fffa5b6864b286a0359eafd0d94b586f301083.jpg"},{"name":"Heal Me Peas","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/fdb8f41d760228cfc41b4b887d3b56d549275565.jpg"},{"name":"Quick-Draw Pod","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/60010fb2bfdc43a00f28109b198a69306ad672a0.jpg"},{"name":"Aspairagus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/323b84401cd1b72a44bc00fcdf67187e1e6b96d3.jpg"},{"name":"Quadsparagus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/f61aee6e8bc64869d26540ed58f5e1daa8804152.jpg"},{"name":"Chick Magnet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/604240/4421ccbbbe2c8a844d0bb371b87bcce18a2e7ee7.jpg"}],"total":73},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/604240/page_